msg: Backout of previous change which is considered ill-advised.  The EntityResolver should not be automatically propagated.  Those wishing to do so should set up a custom URIResolver returning a SAXSource with an appropriate XMLReader.  See discussion and example code in bug 1830 (http://nagoya.apache.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=1830).
